                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "utN19",
                      "name": "h1",
                      "content": "Best Insurance for Families in Tel Aviv: A Complete Guide",
                      "fontFamily": "Source Serif 4",
                      "fontSize": 24,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "69siF",
                      "name": "p1",
                      "content": "Finding the right insurance for your family in Tel Aviv can feel overwhelming. With dozens of providers and hundreds of plans, how do you know which one actually fits your needs? This guide breaks down the top options for families living in Israel’s tech capital.",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Q1rej",
                      "name": "h2",
                      "content": "Why Family Insurance Matters More Than Ever",
                      "fontFamily": "Source Serif 4",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "4gLe3",
                      "name": "p2",
                      "content": "With rising healthcare costs and an increasingly complex regulatory environment, having comprehensive family coverage isn’t just smart — it’s essential. Families in Tel Aviv face unique challenges:",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "uLfOF",
                      "name": "bullets",
                      "content": "•  High cost of living requires robust financial protection\n•  Children’s health needs change rapidly\n•  Dual-income households need disability coverage\n•  Property values demand adequate home insurance",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "GOvBL",
                      "name": "h3",
                      "content": "Top 5 Insurance Providers for Tel Aviv Families",
                      "fontFamily": "Source Serif 4",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ccMUi",
                      "name": "p3",
                      "content": "Based on coverage breadth, customer satisfaction, and value for money, here are our top recommendations for 2026...",
